Former Formula One Champ Kimi Raikkonen May Race in Nascar, Agent Says

-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 
2011-03-29T14:59:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/former-formula-one-champ-kimi-raikkonen-may-race-in-nascar-agent-says.html
Former Formula One champion Kimi
Raikkonen is in talks about joining a Nascar team, his agent
 David Robertson  said by telephone. Robertson declined to
identify the team he was talking to.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
